OL,3,CUS and Iran agree to 'stand down for
OL,4,Cnow' after trading strikes, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe United States and Iran have agreed
OL,8,Fto "stand down for now" after both
OL,9,Fsides exchanged strikes close to the
OL,10,FStrait of Hormuz over the weekend, a
OL,11,FUS official has said.
OL,13,FIran launched drone and missile
OL,14,Fattacks targeting Bahrain and Kuwait
OL,15,Fon Sunday following US airstrikes
OL,16,Fagainst 10 Iranian military targets
OL,17,Fclose to the essential waterway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
