OL,3,CUS and Iran agree to 'stand down for
OL,4,Cnow' after trading strikes, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"Both sides will stand down for now
OL,8,Fand vessels can move freely," a US
OL,9,Fofficial said following the exchange,
OL,10,Faccording to ITV's North American
OL,11,Fpartner CNN.
