OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782769682
OL,3,CUS and Iran agree to 'stand down for
OL,4,Cnow' after trading strikes, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe US and Iran will meet in Doha,
OL,8,FQatar, on Tuesday for more talks,
OL,9,Fanother US official said, amid the
OL,10,Ffragile ceasefire between the two
OL,11,Fnations.
OL,13,FThe crossfire started on Thursday,
OL,14,Fwhen Iran hit a cargo ship in the
OL,15,FStrait of Hormuz, causing the US to
OL,16,Fretaliate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
