PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782769682
OL,3,CUS and Iran agree to 'stand down for
OL,4,Cnow' after trading strikes, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FBoth sides have accused each other of
OL,8,Fviolating their delicate 14-point
OL,9,Finterim agreement, signed on June 17,
OL,10,Fwhich declared that the strait would
OL,11,Fbe reopened for traffic.
OL,13,FA multinational maritime body overseen
OL,14,Fby the US Navy said Saturday it would
OL,15,Fexpand a route near Oman for inbound
OL,16,Fand outbound traffic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
