PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782769682
OL,3,CUS and Iran agree to 'stand down for
OL,4,Cnow' after trading strikes, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FIranian Foreign Minister Abbas
OL,8,FAraghchi on Sunday reiterated the
OL,9,Fclaim the Islamic Republic must govern
OL,10,Fthe strait to the Persian Gulf that
OL,11,Fonce carried a fifth of the world's
OL,12,Foil.
OL,14,F"Any attempt to establish new or
OL,15,Fseparate arrangements from those
OL,16,Fcurrently being carried out by the
OL,17,FIslamic Republic of Iran will only
OL,18,Flead to further complications, delay
OL,19,Fthe reopening of the Strait of Hormuz
OL,20,Fand increase the level of tension,"
OL,21,FAraghchi said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU|D@cO]
