OL,3,CUS and Iran agree to 'stand down for
OL,4,Cnow' after trading strikes, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe strait has long been considered an
OL,8,Finternational waterway despite its
OL,9,Flocation in Iran and Oman's
OL,10,Fterritorial waters.
OL,12,FBahrain said the Iranian strikes
OL,13,Fdamaged a residential building near
OL,14,Fthe international airport, but no one
OL,15,Fwas injured or killed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
