PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782769682
OL,3,CUS and Iran agree to 'stand down for
OL,4,Cnow' after trading strikes, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FBahrain's Foreign Ministry called the
OL,8,Fincident "a dangerous escalation that
OL,9,Freveals that what Tehran is doing is
OL,10,Fnot a passing act, nor an isolated
OL,11,Fincident, but rather a deliberate
OL,12,Fapproach and a systematic pattern of
OL,13,Frepeated aggression".
OL,15,FQatar said a civilian had been killed,
OL,16,Fand another person was hurt by
OL,17,Fshrapnel related to "military
OL,18,Foperations in the area" after a vessel
OL,19,Fdidn't return at its scheduled time on
OL,20,FSaturday, but did not give further
OL,21,Fdetails.
OL,26,@pD@JOUyD@UOU
