OL,3,CUS and Iran agree to 'stand down for
OL,4,Cnow' after trading strikes, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FUS President Donald Trump accused Iran
OL,8,Fof violating the nations' deal and
OL,9,Fwarned of a point where the US may "be
OL,10,Fforced to militarily complete the job"
OL,11,Fon Truth Social.
OL,13,F"If that happens, the Islamic Republic
OL,14,Fof Iran will no longer exist!" Trump
OL,15,Fwrote.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@^O]
