PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782769682
OL,3,CUS and Iran agree to 'stand down for
OL,4,Cnow' after trading strikes, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FTalks between the US and Iran include
OL,8,Farrangements around the strait, the
OL,9,Fremoval of a US blockade on Iranian
OL,10,Fports and sanctions on Iran, and the
OL,11,Ffuture of Iran's stockpile of highly
OL,12,Fenriched uranium.
OL,14,FThe two sides have 60 days from their
OL,15,Fsigning of the memorandum of
OL,16,Funderstanding earlier this month to
OL,17,Fwork out details.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
