OL,3,CUS and Iran agree to 'stand down for
OL,4,Cnow' after trading strikes, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FContinued conflict in Lebanon
OL,8,Fthreatens the agreement, which says
OL,9,Ffighting must end on all fronts before
OL,10,Fcertain issues can be discussed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
